<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text">Although stands typically are not a fire type because of this plant’s moist coastal habitat, fire removes thatch that builds up on the stabilized dunes. <i>Ammophila arenaria </i>sprouts and vigorously grows in the newly exposed sand (Pickart and Sawyer 1998).</div>
